            </daterange>
         </unitdatestructured>
         <abstract id="aspace_c91857b7c6da6b9ebc592a5245744b37">The materials consist of photographs documenting the construction of Timothy Dwight College at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views and photographs of the master's house.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_f8921c128a6856231d2a2da4692a1641">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_d1daaf85960f24fd7648a03ef862befe">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Timothy Dwight College, Yale University, Photographs (RU 602). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_4a941fcafc2551cf8d3ccb096efe1e35">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_ebfe4c3e010e479b1c8186ff84567259">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged in four series: I. Construction Progress Photographs, 1934-1935. II. General Views, 1934-1938. III. Oversize. IV. Slides and transparencies.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_acf634e93f6f004859a6acf36175fbf2">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs documenting the construction of Timothy Dwight College at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views and photographs of the master's house.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
